  <span id="freeText4665327028217753885" style="display:none">This serie has potential.<br />If i was head over heals for the first one; then Cupid must have made it it's soul mission to shoot me with as much arrows as possible because i'm down right in love with this book!<br />It shed a light on Lots of stuff that happened in ODBF that apparently passed right under Ava's nose, The Romance was so fulfilling i swear i had butterflies in my stomach at some points, and with a few tears here and there and a ton of laughs i would say it was perfect.<br />The bromance between Sebastian and Collin, the relationship between Emily and her sister and the matchmaking she was doing behind the curtains only added splendor to this already Amazing book.<br />It also has a Playlist which is Always a plus for me.<br />Although this year has only started i can tell LOVE ME WHILE I'M GONE will be one of my favorite reads in it ♥ I highly recommend you read "Half of me" .</span>
