<div id="review_1467270720" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1467270720" />
    <a title="Jennifer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1865452-jennifer"><img alt="Jennifer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1309927806p2/1865452.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1467270720?book_show_action=true">Dec 12, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jennifer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jennifer" href="/user/show/1865452-jennifer">Jennifer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1467270720" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11150604588835498481">I hope your ready for an emotional roller coaster because this is what you receive as soon as you start reading this AMAZING novel. Their will be times where you want to cry with both An and Collin and there will be times where you want to tell in frustration and excitement!!!!! This is a great romance novel that shows the difficulty and work that has to be put into a relationship especially when you have many things that are going wrong in your life. Em&apos;s and Collins relationship make you feel </span>
  <span id="freeText11150604588835498481" style="display:none">I hope your ready for an emotional roller coaster because this is what you receive as soon as you start reading this AMAZING novel. Their will be times where you want to cry with both An and Collin and there will be times where you want to tell in frustration and excitement!!!!! This is a great romance novel that shows the difficulty and work that has to be put into a relationship especially when you have many things that are going wrong in your life. Em's and Collins relationship make you feel like you want to go to both of them and help them figure out how to fix things between them . Mrs Diana Scott did in amazing job in inputing OUR DEMONS BEST FRIENDS INTO this novel because it give you a better insight into Em's and Collins relationship. Now only dia Mrs Diana Scott do the above but she wrote this novel in such a way that make the reader feel as if they are there experiencing what Em and Collin are experiencing. Honestly could not have been a better novel. To me it was perfect in everyway. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11150604588835498481" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

