<span id="freeTextContainer1621518288476041208">I love this book! It&apos;s based in the same setting as &quot;Our demons, best friends&quot; and tells Collin&apos;s and Emily&apos;s story. Diana Scott manages to create heartbreaking lovestorys with a happy ending and the books are a very good and quick read. I didn&apos;t want to put it away at all. I cried a few times while I was reading because sometimes I could really relate to feelings and situations. But that&apos;s what makes her books so wonderful, they&apos;re so close to the feelings of the reader. Thank you for this amaz</span>
  <span id="freeText1621518288476041208" style="display:none">I love this book! It's based in the same setting as "Our demons, best friends" and tells Collin's and Emily's story. Diana Scott manages to create heartbreaking lovestorys with a happy ending and the books are a very good and quick read. I didn't want to put it away at all. I cried a few times while I was reading because sometimes I could really relate to feelings and situations. But that's what makes her books so wonderful, they're so close to the feelings of the reader. Thank you for this amazing story Diana!! </span>
